          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-1" n="1">Quoth the thief to the dog; `let me into your door,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-2" n="2">And I'll give you these delicate bits:'</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-3" n="3">Quoth the dog, `I should then be more villain than you're,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-4" n="4">And besides must be out of my wits:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-5" n="5"><lb/>`Your delicate bits will not serve me a meal,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-6" n="6">But my master each day gives me bread;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-7" n="7">You'll fly when you get what you come here to steal,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-8" n="8">And I must be hanged in your stead.'</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-9" n="9"><lb/>The stockjobber thus, from ChangeÂ·Alley goes down,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-10" n="10">And tips you the freeman a wink;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-11" n="11">`Let me have but your vote to serve for the town,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-12" n="12">And here is a guinea to drink.'</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-13" n="13"><lb/>Said the freeman, `your guinea tonight would be spent,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-14" n="14">Your offers of bribery cease;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-15" n="15">I'll vote for my landlord to whom I pay rent,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-16" n="16">Or else I may forfeit my lease.'</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-17" n="17"><lb/>From London they come, silly people to chouse,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-18" n="18">Their lands and their faces unknown;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-19" n="19">Who'd vote a rogue into the parliament-house,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-395-ROGP-line-20" n="20">That would turn a man out of his own?</l>
          </lg>
